
java -jar selenuim-server-standalone -role hub -host 127.0.0.1 -port 4444 

java -jar selenuim-server-standalone -role hub



java -jar selenuim-server-standalone -role webdriver -hub http://localhost:4444/grid/register -port 5555 -browser browserName=firefox

java -jar selenuim-server-standalone -role webdriver -hub http://localhost:4444/grid/register -port 5555 -browser browserName=firefox

java -jar selenuim-server-standalone -role webdriver -hub http://localhost:4444/grid/register -port 5555 -browser browserName=firefox -browser browserName=iexplore -browser browserName=chrome 

java -jar selenuim-server-standalone -role webdriver -hub http://localhost:4444/grid/register -port 5555 -browser browserName=firefox -browser browserName=iexplore -browser browserName=chrome.maxInstances=3


Setting up chrome and IE DRIVERS

Setting up chrome Driver

-Dwebdriver.chrome.driver=C:\selenium\chromedriver.exe

Setting up IE Driver

-Dwebdriver.chrome.driver=C:\selenium\IEDriverServer.exe

Final Command

java -Dwebdriver.chrome.driver=C:\selenium\chromedriver.exe -Dwebdriver.chrome.driver=C:\selenium\IEDriverServer.exe  -jar selenuim-server-standalone -role webdriver -hub http://localhost:4444/grid/register -port 5555 -browser browserName=firefox -browser browserName=iexplore -browser browserName=chrome.maxInstances=3

